OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772025560
OL,3,CMoment people smuggler is stopped by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FFootage has been released of the
OL,7,Fmoment a man from Reading who arranged
OL,8,Fthe transport of Vietnamese migrants
OL,9,Fto the UK was stopped by police.
OL,11,FDuc Quang Ta, 36, has been found
OL,12,Fguilty of people smuggling and money
OL,13,Flaundering.
OL,15,FHe was stopped by police in Surrey in
OL,16,F2020.
OL,18,FHe was part of a crime group which hid
OL,19,Fmigrants in the backs of lorries which
OL,20,Ftravelled to the UK via ferries or the
OL,21,FChannel Tunnel.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
