PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772025560
OL,3,CMoment people smuggler is stopped by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FVietnamese national Ta was found to be
OL,7,Finvolved in the transport, or
OL,8,Fattempted transport, of migrants on 16
OL,9,Foccasions between 18 August and 6
OL,10,FSeptember 2020.
OL,12,FA total of 22 people were successfully
OL,13,Fsmuggled into the UK during this
OL,14,Ftimeframe, although the offending
OL,15,Fperiod is suspected of being much
OL,16,Fwider.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
