OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772025560
OL,3,CMoment people smuggler is stopped by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FTa was the front seat passenger in a
OL,7,FBMW X5 stopped by Surrey Police and
OL,8,FThames Valley Police on the M25 near
OL,9,FLeatherhead in Surrey on 3 September
OL,10,F2020.
OL,12,FHe was arrested as an illegal
OL,13,Fimmigrant, with police also finding
OL,14,F#55,020 in cash which had been stuffed
OL,15,Finside a plastic bag in the rear
OL,16,Fpassenger footwell, and a further
OL,17,F#1,000 in Ta's pocket.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772025560
OL,3,CMoment people smuggler is stopped by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FThey also seized a phone, which was
OL,7,Flater forensically examined and showed
OL,8,Fmessages from Ta about #56,000 in cash
OL,9,Fa few hours before his arrest.
OL,11,FThese showed that he was heading to
OL,12,FKent to hand the money to co-
OL,13,Fconspirators who had arranged for a
OL,14,Fnumber of migrants to be smuggled into
OL,15,Fthe UK in the back of an HGV.
OL,17,FIt appears that the plan had been for
OL,18,Fthe immigrants to be delivered to
OL,19,FGillingham where they would then be
OL,20,Ftaken away to safe houses elsewhere in
OL,21,Fthe UK in cars.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772025560
OL,3,CMoment people smuggler is stopped by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FTa worked with the wider crime group
OL,7,Fto match would be immigrants with
OL,8,Fslots in lorries which were about to
OL,9,Fcross from Europe to the UK. He acted
OL,10,Flike an agent or operations manager,
OL,11,Forganising drivers, lorries, safe
OL,12,Fhouses and immigrants.
OL,14,FThe group used slang on encrypted
OL,15,Fsocial media apps to avoid detection.
OL,17,FHe'll be sentenced in July.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
