OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772025560
OL,3,CMoment people smuggler is stopped by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,FNCA senior investigating officer David
OL,7,FCushway said: "Ta and Sardarzehi were
OL,8,Fpart of an organised immigration crime
OL,9,Fgroup that exploited migrants at every
OL,10,Fstep of their dangerous journeys to
OL,11,Fthe UK, all for the sake of profit.
OL,13,F"They placed these people at enormous
OL,14,Frisk by putting them in HGVs, with the
OL,15,Flanguage they used to describe them
OL,16,Findicative of the disdain they held
OL,17,Fthem in.
OL,26,@oD@OOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
