PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772025560
OL,3,CMoment people smuggler is stopped by
OL,4,Cpolice
OL,6,F"Cases like these harden the National
OL,7,FCrime Agency's resolve to bring
OL,8,Findividuals like Ta and Sardarzehi
OL,9,Fbefore the courts and disrupt the
OL,10,Forganised crime groups behind this
OL,11,Fevil trade."
